Title: ChIPAnalyzer
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ryan Denniston
Maintainer: Ryan Denniston <ryan.denniston@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: A package for the analysis of ChIP-seq peaks, including 
  tools for investigating G-quadruplexes and methylation data in the 
  vicinity of peaks.
